*** CONTENTS ***

1. INPUT AND OUTPUT

1.1) => Write a program in C++ to find Size of fundamental data types.
1.2) => Write a program in C++ to check the upper and lower limits of integer, double, float. 
1.3) => Write a program in C++ to test the Type Casting. 
1.4) => Write a program in C++ to print the code (ASCII code / Unicode code etc.) of a given character.
1.5) => Write a C++ program to check the largest number among three given integers.
 
